x10.matrix.dist

Class DupSparseMatrix

  • x10.matrix.Matrix
    • x10.matrix.dist.DupSparseMatrix

  • public class DupSparseMatrix
extends Matrix
    Implementation of duplicated sparse matrix. All duplicated sparse matrices are stored in DistArray. Distribution of dense matrices is unique, one duplicated copy is mapped to one place.
